<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I Hukdampau nungsul chuh zui zel dingin,
 I Hukdampau leh Lalpen chuh zuiin;
 I hindan leh Amah umdan pha la leng,
 Kipak leh lawptak in la chu sai tiu.

[V2]
 Hukdampa nungsul zuia chieh chuh a hawih na e,
 Vak achun chieh in, vak achun chieh in;
 Hukdampa nungsul zuia chieh chuh ahawih na e,
 Lamdik ah ei pui.

[V3]
 2. Amah ei Puipa kawm nai achun chieh in,
 Chiehmang dinga thepa I um lai un;
 Ei panpih ding A ban thahat a kinga'n,
 Kipakin ni cheng in chawian hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Ginnan I hukdam pau nungsul chuh zuiin,
 I Puipa ei puihna chuh zui zelin;
 Lalpen chu &quot;A hawihna a&quot; I muh tiengleh,
 Kipak takin A kawm ah um tai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>WALKING IN THE LIGTH</title>
<hymn_number>415</hymn_number>
</song>